descriptionHtml:
This is an action game that reproduces the fierce Atlantic naval battle, and it will enable you to fight in the Second World War navigating famous warship of that age.

You can be a captain of legendary battleships such as Bismarck, U-Boat, Hood, destroyers, submarines etc.,

creator: My School Life
descriptionHtml:
It's a warship action game that deals with the fierce Second World War Atlantic War, and will allow you to directly coordinate warships.

Take part in the battle in the ocean, command and control naval warships in naval battles to sink enemy battleships.

Warship : World War 2 - The Atlantic War is a naval battle action game that allows you to experience the maritime strategies and tactics of the time on mobile.

Navy warships that fought in the Atlantic Ocean were implemented on mobile and tablets to faithfully recreate the naval battleship of that time.

Game Features:
- You can be the captain of a naval battleship fleet that controls warships, cruisers, destroyers, and submarines during World War II.
- Use a variety of naval combat weapons, including torpedoes, guns, lightning and mines.
- Be the captain of the legendary German and British battleships Bismarck, U-Boat, and Hood, and engage in the Battle of the Atlantic Ocean.
- Facebook login support

You can download it for free now.

CAUTION:
- A stable Internet environment is needed to enjoy Warship : World War II The Atlantic War.(This may result in network charges)
- To use the app, consent is required for personal information and service terms and conditions and end-user license agreements.
- In-game ads are included.
- In-game in-app items are included.
- This game provides in-game items for a fee. If you don't want to purchase paid content, please restrict your purchase by setting Google Play 'Configuration' to enter 'Password'.
